      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>diced tomato</strong>,<strong> drained sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a bowl</p><p>Squeeze over the juice of your <strong>lime</strong> and drizzle in 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season generously with both <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> corn salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/991.-step-3-x200.jpg",
