          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/991.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>blackened haddock bites</strong> over the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong> with the <strong>corn salsa</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>lime wedges </strong>and drizzle with the <strong>spicy mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
